+## Hilal Welcome - Privacy Levels
+
+hilal-welcome-privacy-standard-label = Balanced
+hilal-welcome-privacy-standard-badge = LibreWolf-like
+hilal-welcome-privacy-standard-desc = RFP, strict tracking protection, HTTPS-only, URL cleanup, WebGL off, and cookie/cache cleanup on close.
+hilal-welcome-privacy-standard-detail = WebRTC stays enabled for compatibility, with local leak surfaces reduced.
+
+hilal-welcome-privacy-strict-label = Strict
+hilal-welcome-privacy-strict-badge = Less compatible
+hilal-welcome-privacy-strict-desc = Adds First Party Isolation on top of Balanced and disables WebRTC entirely.
+hilal-welcome-privacy-strict-detail = Video calls and some sign-in flows may break.
+
+hilal-welcome-privacy-extreme-label = Maximum
+hilal-welcome-privacy-extreme-badge = Not Tor
+hilal-welcome-privacy-extreme-desc = Adds JavaScript, camera, microphone, location, and history blocking on top of Strict.
+hilal-welcome-privacy-extreme-detail = Does not hide your IP address; many modern sites may not work as expected.
